### Pruebas para los endpoints del Dashboard de Progreso
### Asegúrate de tener datos de progreso registrados para el usuario

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@userId = 48

### 1. Dashboard completo - Período mensual (por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 2. Dashboard completo - Período semanal
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}&period=WEEK
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 3. Dashboard completo - Período personalizado
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}&period=CUSTOM&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 4. Dashboard completo - Período trimestral
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}&period=QUARTER
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 5. Dashboard rápido diario
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/quick/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 6. Análisis de tendencias - Semanal
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/analytics/trends/{{userId}}?period=WEEK
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 7. Análisis de tendencias - Mensual
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/analytics/trends/{{userId}}?period=MONTH
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 8. Análisis de rendimiento - Semanal
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/analytics/performance/{{userId}}?period=WEEK
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 9. Análisis de rendimiento - Mensual
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/analytics/performance/{{userId}}?period=MONTH
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 10. Alertas y recomendaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/alerts/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 11. Resumen ejecutivo
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/summary/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Casos de error para probar validaciones

### 12. Dashboard sin userId (debe fallar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 13. Dashboard con userId inválido (debe fallar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/quick/0
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 14. Usuario inexistente (debe manejar graciosamente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/quick/999999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 15. Período inválido (debe usar por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}&period=INVALID_PERIOD
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### 16. Fechas personalizadas inválidas
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard/complete?userId={{userId}}&period=CUSTOM&startDate=invalid-date&endDate=2025-01-31
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
